data.title: How easy is it to predict lake-effect snow in the Buffalo region?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): Well predicting how much and exactly when can get complicated.

But Buffalo often gets lake effect snow. So I would just ask myself,

Has Lake Erie frozen?

If no, then lake effect snow is plausible.
